---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frenchify Beginner Program — Sign-Up for Free">
<!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-blue-50 full-bleed-section-ghl">
    <div class="ghl-row mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Beginner Program — Your First Step Towards Canada PR
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        This is your <span class="font-semibold">first step</span> to learn French for Canada PR.
        Sign up for this program to build a solid base and understand the key aspects of the French language.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
        <a href="https://learn.frenchifywithvyom.com/l/3f67c30cab" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow">
          Sign me up for Free (Worth 150$)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MODULES -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 bg-white full-bleed-section-ghl" style="padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;">
    <div class="ghl-row mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What You’ll Cover in This Preview</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Get oriented with the core concepts of the French language. You’ll understand how to build sentences, follow a clear weekly plan, and finish with a quick check of your understanding at the end.
      </p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-left">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Grammar</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Articles, pronouns, sentence order.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Vocabulary</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Greetings, introductions, family, nationalities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Pronunciation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Key sounds, vowels, the French “R”.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Reading</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Short texts to build comprehension.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Listening</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Mini introductions + guided answers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Writing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Compose your “Présentez-vous”.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Speaking</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Record and refine a short intro.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1 text-blue-700">Final Unit Test</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Quick check to confirm progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SHORT VALUE REMINDER -->
  <section class="py-8 px-6 bg-gray-50 full-bleed-section-ghl">
    <div class="ghl-row mx-auto">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        By the end, you’ll know the flow of Frenchify A1, have the base of the language, and a weekly plan you can actually follow — with a final unit test to validate your understanding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section id="cta" class="py-14 px-6 bg-white full-bleed-section-ghl">
    <div class="ghl-row mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Get Started Today</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Start learning French today for Free
      </p>
      <a href="https://learn.frenchifywithvyom.com/l/3f67c30cab" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg shadow">
        Begin My Free Access
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }

    html {
      overflow-x: hidden;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 100%;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
